    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The engine has significant performance issues and requires a major overhaul, while the transmission is slipping and inconsistent. The body shows heavy wear with noticeable rust, multiple dents, and faded paint. The interior is also in rough shape, with torn upholstery and several non-functional electronic components. This car would be best suited as a project for a dedicated mechanic or as a source for spare parts.",
